"title": "5173: outward appearance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5173: outward appearance",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>That which is visible on the outside may reveal the true person, but is sometimes misleading. Judging by it and boasting in it are typical of sinful humanity. God sees the inner reality.</p>\n<h2>Outward appearance can reveal the truth</h2>\n<h3>Spiritually</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:16-Matt7:20\">MAT 7:16–7:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:43-Luke6:45\">LUK 6:43–6:45</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">MAT 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:33-Matt12:37\">MAT 12:33–12:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:8\">JHN 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:17-Jas2:18\">JAS 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Emotionally</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:13\">PRO 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:16-1Sam1:18\">1SA 1:16–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:22\">PRO 17:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:1\">ECC 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5-Dan5:6\">DAN 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22\">MRK 10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Outward appearance can be deceptive</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:25-Matt23:28\">MAT 23:25–23:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:2-Isa53:3\">ISA 53:2–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">MAT 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:39-Luke11:41\">LUK 11:39–11:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2CO 11:13–11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:23\">COL 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:2\">HEB 13:2</a></p>\n<h2>While people may judge by outward appearance, God does not</h2>\n<h3>People take note of outward appearance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:23-John7:24\">JHN 7:23–7:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:14-Luke16:15\">LUK 16:14–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:15\">JHN 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:7\">2CO 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>God looks at the heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:6-1Sam16:7\">1SA 16:6–16:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:39\">1KI 8:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:30\">2CH 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:1-Ps139:2\">PSA 139:1–139:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:2\">PRO 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:2\">PRO 21:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:3–11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:6\">GAL 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:23\">REV 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>The folly of boasting in outward appearance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:45-Luke20:47\">LUK 20:45–20:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:2\">MAT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16\">MAT 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:12\">2CO 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:12\">GAL 6:12</a></p>\n<h2>What is unseen is more important than outward appearance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:16–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:6\">PSA 51:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10-Ps147:11\">PSA 147:10–147:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:28-Rom2:29\">ROM 2:28–2:29</a></p>\n<h2>Beautiful physical appearance</h2>\n<h3>Examples of the problems and opportunities caused by beautiful outward appearance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:11-Gen12:15\">GEN 12:11–12:15</a> <em>Sarah's beauty led to Abraham's folly</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:6-Gen39:7\">GEN 39:6–39:7</a> <em>Joseph's handsome appearance led to his being tempted by Potiphar's wife</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:2\">1SA 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:12\">1SA 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:3\">1SA 25:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:3\">2SA 11:2–11:3</a> <em>Bathsheba's beauty tempted David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:25-2Sam14:26\">2SA 14:25–14:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:10-Esth1:11\">EST 1:10–1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:7\">EST 2:7</a> <em>Esther's beauty was an opportunity for God.</em></p>\n<h3>The cultivation of inner beauty encouraged</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:3-1Pet3:5\">1PE 3:3–3:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:9-1Tim2:10\">1TI 2:9–2:10</a></p>",
